frames.caption: A cheerful boy sits between a rabbit and a mouse on a bus, waving happily. The trio is seated on a purple bench, with the bus interior painted in warm yellow tones. Through the windows, a scenic countryside with a white fence and lush greenery is visible.
frames.description: The scene takes place inside a moving bus, where a young boy and two animated animals are enjoying a ride. The setting is bright and cheerful, suggesting a fun journey through the countryside.
